title: Northgate needs win today at Ola to clinch state berth
text:
Northgate needs win today at Ola to clinch state berth Friday, October 09, 2015 Comments 
After defeating subregion foes McIntosh and Starr’s Mill to open the Region 4- tournament on Wednesday Northgate need a win today at Ola to clinch a state berth and further its 2015 season in the Class playoffs. 
The Lady Vikings, who saw a streak of state playoff appearances end last season, open the second day of tournament play against host Ola at 10 a.m. 
A win advances Northgate to a 2 p.m. game, while a loss forces a loser’s bracket contest directly afterward at 12 p.m. More
